changes: The Chronokeep Portal settings window now has an update button and some options have moved.
The previous change adding the reader name to the raw chip reads data page has been reverted.
The constructor for a Chip Read from a Chronokeep Portal device now takes the box name in to properly identify it on the Raw Reads data page.
Due to changes in the Version 1.1.0 version of the Chronokeep Portal software, some code has been removed from the API for said boxes.
Due to changes in the Version 1.1.0 version of the Chronokeep Portal software, some options on the settings page for said boxes have been removed.
